project_descr: This Plan seeks to strengthen UNDP Colombia’s capacity to provide technical assistance to national and subnational partners in Rule of Law areas, set up spaces of dialogue and expand and consolidate a UNDP integrated portfolio in Rule of Law

outputs.output_descr: The Initiation Plan intents to achieve an integrated RoL portfolio/programme, capitalizing on current projects (i.e. citizen security at the local level and local justice systems) while expanding the scope and impact of interventions
donor_name: SWISS AGENCY FOR DEVELOPMENT AND COOPERATION - SDC

project_title: preparation rule of law programme colombia
